thread.title: Wildcat Ranch

title: Wildcat Ranch
text: By The Union Democrat Sports Department October 01, 2015 01:00 am Sonora Wildcat Jackson McIlroy nears the finish of Wednesday's meet. Maggie Beck / Union Democrat, Copyright 2015. For the first time in nearly 50 years, Sonora High hosted a cross-country meet.On Wednesday afternoon,Wildcat Ranch had its inaugural race in the third Mother Lode League meet of the season. The course was designed by 2014 Sonora graduate Steven Grolle and completed by current Wildcat Patrick McConnell. Follow UnionDemocrat.com
